# Short Circuit

> [!word] Short Circuit
> An electrical circuit that has **infinately low [resistance](20220408115601-resistance.md)** (approx. to 0) than any preexisting paths between the same nodes, which allows an **_excessive (Infinite) [current](20220408104411-current.md)_** flowing through.

![46b595550277fe9d98929b743642b1df](data:image/png;base64,)

> [!note]
> Short Circuit has the potential to damage components.
